
Creating a Laravel 5 Package

* Create a git repository
* Create a src and tests folder
* download https://raw.githubusercontent.com/laravel/laravel/master/phpunit.xml
* composer init

- Would you like to define your dependencies (require) interactively [yes]? yes
php
laravel/framework


- Would you like to define your dev dependencies (require-dev) interactively [yes]? yes
laravel/laravel
phpunit/phpunit


Define your version or use latest when searching.

Edit composer.json to define your autoloads and a script to shortcut phpunit.

"autoload": {
    "psr-4": {
        "Askedio\\LaravelValidatorFilter\\": "src/"
    }
},
"autoload-dev": {
    "psr-4": {
        "Askedio\\LaravelValidatorFilter\\Tests\\" : "tests"
    }
},
"scripts": {
    "test": "vendor/bin/phpunit"
},



composer install


mkdir src/Providers
copy https://raw.githubusercontent.com/laravel/laravel/master/app/Providers/AppServiceProvider.php

change name and namespace


for tests you can copy
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/laravel/laravel/master/tests/TestCase.php

change name to BaseTestCase and add namespace





